categories: Category:Battles of the Yuuzhan Vong War

nodes.text: A skirmish occurred on Csilla in 28 ABY, between a Galactic Alliance team on the hunt for Zonama Sekot, and rogue Chiss elements under the command of Ganet. Although the Chiss managed to bring the ice barge the group were traveling with to a halt, the Jedi of the team defeated the snow-fliers that were sent against them. Concurrently, Jacen Solo foiled Chief Navigator Peita Aabe's attempt to kidnap Wynssa Fel.
